data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 full bathrooms plus BONUS ROOM sits in East Golden Hills overlooking the Nature Park and Tom Sawyer Lake. The home has 2 bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom upstairs and another bedroom, bathroom and bonus room downstairs. The living room has a real fireplace, newer vinyl plank flooring and a sliding glass door that opens up to a small patio. 2 car attached garage, a nice sized storage shed with electricity and almost a quarter of an acre of low maintenance landscaping. Home does have central heat and AC.
